articleList.title: Introduce
articleList.desc: When you understand life and self are not used to overcome but to get along! You will understand some things although not reasonable, but you must believe, they are strong, you must rely on!

articleList.title: 托尼托尼·乔巴
articleList.desc: 乔巴的能力本身继承了冬岛的各种医术知识，加上自己在两年间对药草的研究，还有自己本身的天赋，乔巴的医术已经非常强大，总感觉缺少了点什么？有没有可能再进一步提升医术，毕竟是船医啊！
